data.description: Beautiful residence offers innate charm and great style. This home features two versatile living areas or game room, exceptional kitchen equipped with ample storage, walk-in pantry, formal and casual dining areas, primary suite with ensuite bath and walk-in closet along with three additional bedrooms  that provide flexibility for a growing family, guests or home office. Located on a culdesac, the outdoor space is complete with a covered porch, privacy fence, and is situated on an oversized lot and offers convenience to restaurants and shopping.
